---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="DTH Recharge Online | TrueCred Loan Expert">

<!-- Page Hero -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="breadcrumb">
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <span class="sep"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i></span>
        <a href="/pages/recharge-bills">Recharge &amp; Bills</a>
        <span class="sep"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i></span>
        <span>DTH Recharge</span>
      </div>
      <h1>DTH Recharge Online</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">Recharge your DTH connection instantly — Tata Play, Airtel Digital TV, Dish TV, Sun Direct, and D2H. Browse plans and never miss your favourite shows.</p>
      <div class="hero-highlights">
        <div class="highlight-item">
          <i class="fas fa-satellite-dish"></i> Providers: All Major
        </div>
        <div class="highlight-item">
          <i class="fas fa-bolt"></i> Activation: Instant
        </div>
        <div class="highlight-item">
          <i class="fas fa-tags"></i> Best Plan Deals
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Page Content -->
  <section class="page-content">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-grid">

        <!-- Main Content -->
        <div class="content-main">
          <h2>Recharge Your DTH Connection Instantly</h2>
          <p>Keep your entertainment running without interruption by recharging your DTH connection through TrueCred Loan Expert. We support all major DTH providers in India — Tata Play, Airtel Digital TV, Dish TV, Sun Direct, and D2H Videocon. Browse available channel packs, compare plans, and recharge in seconds.</p>
          <p>Our platform displays the latest DTH plans with channel lists so you can pick the perfect pack for your family. Whether you need regional channels, sports packs, HD upgrades, or basic entertainment bundles — find and activate them instantly.</p>

          <!-- DTH Plans Comparison -->
          <h3>Popular DTH Plans Comparison</h3>
          <div class="table-responsive" style="overflow-x:auto; margin: 24px 0 40px;">
            <table style="width:100%; border-collapse:collapse; min-width:600px;">
              <thead>
                <tr style="background: var(--primary); color: #fff;">
                  <th style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:left;">Provider</th>
                  <th style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:left;">Pack Name</th>
                  <th style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:center;">Channels</th>
                  <th style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:center;">HD</th>
                  <th style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:center;">Monthly Price</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; font-weight:600;">Tata Play</td>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px;">Super Value Pack</td>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:center;">350+</td>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:center; color: green;"><i class="fas fa-check"></i></td>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:center; font-weight:700; color: var(--primary);">₹449</td>
                </tr>
                <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb; background: #f9fafb;">
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; font-weight:600;">Airtel Digital TV</td>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px;">Premium HD Pack</td>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:center;">300+</td>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:center; color: green;"><i class="fas fa-check"></i></td>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:center; font-weight:700; color: var(--primary);">₹425</td>
                </tr>
                <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; font-weight:600;">Dish TV</td>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px;">Super Family HD</td>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:center;">280+</td>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:center; color: green;"><i class="fas fa-check"></i></td>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:center; font-weight:700; color: var(--primary);">₹399</td>
                </tr>
                <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb; background: #f9fafb;">
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; font-weight:600;">Sun Direct</td>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px;">Elite Pack</td>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:center;">250+</td>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:center; color: green;"><i class="fas fa-check"></i></td>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:center; font-weight:700; color: var(--primary);">₹375</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; font-weight:600;">D2H</td>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px;">Gold HD Sports</td>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:center;">320+</td>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:center; color: green;"><i class="fas fa-check"></i></td>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:center; font-weight:700; color: var(--primary);">₹435</td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>

          <!-- Benefits -->
          <h2>Why Recharge DTH Through TrueCred?</h2>
          <ul class="feature-list">
            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>All DTH Providers:</strong> Tata Play, Airtel Digital TV, Dish TV, Sun Direct, and D2H — all supported on one platform</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Instant Activation:</strong> Your DTH pack is activated within seconds of payment, ensuring zero downtime</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Plan Comparison:</strong> Compare channel packs across providers to find the best value for your budget</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Add-On Packs:</strong> Recharge for sports, movies, regional, kids, or HD add-on channel packs separately</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Auto-Renewal Support:</strong> Set up auto-pay so your DTH never expires — enjoy uninterrupted entertainment</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Recharge History:</strong> Track all past DTH recharges and set reminders for upcoming renewals</li>
          </ul>

          <!-- How It Works -->
          <h2>How to Recharge Your DTH</h2>
          <p>Recharge your DTH in 4 quick steps.</p>
          <div class="steps-grid">
            <div class="step-card">
              <div class="step-num">1</div>
              <h4>Select DTH Provider</h4>
              <p>Choose your DTH operator — Tata Play, Airtel, Dish TV, Sun Direct, or D2H.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step-card">
              <div class="step-num">2</div>
              <h4>Enter Subscriber ID</h4>
              <p>Enter your DTH subscriber ID or registered mobile number to fetch your account.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step-card">
              <div class="step-num">3</div>
              <h4>Choose Plan &amp; Pay</h4>
              <p>Browse available packs or enter a custom amount, then pay via UPI, card, or net banking.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step-card">
              <div class="step-num">4</div>
              <h4>Instant Activation</h4>
              <p>Your selected channels are activated instantly. Confirmation sent via SMS and email.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Page CTA -->
          <div class="page-cta">
            <div>
              <h3>Explore More Bill Payment Services</h3>
              <p>Mobile recharge, electricity bills, FASTag, LPG bookings — all from one platform.</p>
            </div>
            <a href="/pages/recharge-bills" class="btn btn-outline">All Services <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Sidebar -->
        <div class="content-sidebar">
          <!-- DTH Recharge Form -->
          <div class="sidebar-card">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-satellite-dish" style="color: var(--primary); margin-right: 6px;"></i> DTH Recharge</h3>
            <form class="sidebar-form" onsubmit="return false;">
              <div class="form-group">
                <select class="form-input">
                  <option value="">Select DTH Provider</option>
                  <option value="tataplay">Tata Play</option>
                  <option value="airtel">Airtel Digital TV</option>
                  <option value="dishtv">Dish TV</option>
                  <option value="sundirect">Sun Direct</option>
                  <option value="d2h">D2H (Videocon)</option>
                </select>
              </div>
              <div class="form-group">
                <input type="text" class="form-input" placeholder="Subscriber ID / RMN">
              </div>
              <div class="form-group">
                <select class="form-input">
                  <option value="">Select Plan Type</option>
                  <option value="monthly">Monthly Pack</option>
                  <option value="quarterly">Quarterly Pack</option>
                  <option value="annual">Annual Pack</option>
                  <option value="addon">Add-On Pack</option>
                  <option value="custom">Custom Amount</option>
                </select>
              </div>
              <div class="form-group">
                <input type="number" class="form-input" placeholder="Amount (₹)">
              </div>
              <button class="btn btn-primary btn-block" style="width:100%;justify-content:center;">
                Recharge Now <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i>
              </button>
            </form>
          </div>

          <!-- Quick Links -->
          <div class="sidebar-card">
            <h3>Other Services</h3>
            <div class="sidebar-links">
              <a href="/pages/mobile-recharge"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i> Mobile Recharge</a>
              <a href="/pages/electricity-bill"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i> Electricity Bill Payment</a>
              <a href="/pages/fastag-recharge"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i> FASTag Recharge</a>
              <a href="/pages/lpg-gas-booking"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i> LPG Gas Booking</a>
              <a href="/pages/loan-emi-payment"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i> Loan EMI Payment</a>
              <a href="/pages/credit-score"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i> Free Credit Score</a>
              <a href="/pages/personal-loan"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i> Personal Loan</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section class="faq-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-tag">FAQs</span>
        <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <p>Common questions about DTH recharge on TrueCred.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-list">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question">
            Which DTH providers can I recharge on TrueCred?
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">
              You can recharge all major DTH providers in India including Tata Play (formerly Tata Sky), Airtel Digital TV, Dish TV, Sun Direct, and D2H (Videocon). All plans — monthly, quarterly, annual, and add-on packs — are available for each provider.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question">
            Where can I find my DTH subscriber ID?
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">
              Your DTH subscriber ID (also called customer ID or viewing card number) can be found on your set-top box, in the original purchase receipt, or by navigating to the "My Account" section on your DTH provider's app/website. You can also use your registered mobile number to look up your account on TrueCred.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question">
            How quickly is the DTH recharge activated?
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">
              DTH recharges through TrueCred are activated instantly — usually within 10-30 seconds of successful payment. Your channels will start working immediately. In case of provider-side delays, activation may take up to 15 minutes.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question">
            Can I recharge only specific add-on channel packs?
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">
              Yes, you can recharge individual add-on packs such as sports channels, movie channels, regional language packs, kids channels, and HD upgrades. Simply select your provider, choose "Add-On Pack" as the plan type, and browse available add-ons for your subscription.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question">
            Is it cheaper to do an annual DTH recharge vs monthly?
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">
              Yes, most DTH providers offer significant discounts on annual and semi-annual plans compared to monthly recharges. You can save anywhere from 10% to 20% by choosing longer validity packs. TrueCred shows both monthly and annual pricing so you can easily compare the savings.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer -->

</BaseLayout>
